S.FORM: Dexter Boney nalecuhan i Wilmington, Delaware, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. 4 bulad 27 demiad, 1970 a mihca, Dexter Boney, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
